               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra Yoḥannǝs Maṭmǝq “Miracles of John the Baptist”: 13 miracles
                     (fols. 2ra-25vb).</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="2ra" to="25vb"/>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6166MiraclesJohnBaptist">Taʾammǝra Yoḥannǝs Maṭmǝq
                        “Miracles of John the Baptist”: 13 miracles</title>
                  
                     
                     <note>- The miracles are partly numbered (፫-፬, ፮-፲፫).</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
               <physDesc>
