                        <condition key="deficient">The Ms. is worn.
 The front board broken and
                           crudely repaired.
 The original sewing is missing; the Ms. was
                           crudely resewn with recent threads.
 First fols. are damaged by
                           insects/rodents at the outer margins.</condition>
                     </supportDesc>
                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout columns="2" writtenLines="15">
                           <note>- On <locus target="#19r">19r-v</locus> and <locus target="#26r">19r-v</locus>, the scribe switched to
                              one column layout.</note>
                           <dimensions unit="mm">
                              <height>130</height>
                              <width>102</width>
                              <dim type="intercolumn">8</dim>
                           </dimensions>
                           <dimensions type="margin">
                              <dim type="top">20</dim>
